# Controllers

## PageController

### Routes publiques

. `/`

- `/a-propos`

. `/gallerie`

. `/gallerie/:category`

. `/contact`

. `/login`


## ProductCategoryController

### Routes publiques

- `/product/:categorie`

### Routes privées

- `/admin/categories`
- `/admin/categories/ajouter`
- `/admin/categories/:id/details`
- `/admin/categories/:id/modifier`
- `/admin/categories/:id/supprimer`


## ProductController

### Routes publiques

- `/products`
- `/products/:id`

### Routes privées

- `/admin/projets`
- `/admin/projets/ajouter`
- `/admin/projets/:id/details`
- `/admin/projets/:id/modifier`
- `/admin/projets/:id/supprimer`



## MediaController

### Routes privées

- `/admin/medias`
- `/admin/medias/ajouter`
- `/admin/medias/:id/supprimer`
